Important Note for Next Developer:
- Keep this file aligned with next.config.js i18n locales and SEO.js alternate
  URL generation. Default English URLs intentionally do not use /en.
- Add new public product pages here when they are ready for indexing.

Last Modified: v1.0 - Initial multilingual sitemap
============================================
-->
